         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">24/2/91 ¶  ¶ I am very grateful to you, dear Mr Tepper, and so also particularly this time to your young son for the consignment of the  ¶ Adansonia ¶  fruits. ¶  They come just now at the right time....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">91.02.24a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">24/2/91</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sehr dankbar bin ich Ihnen, lieber Herr Tepper, u so auch besonders diesmal Ihrem jungen Sohne für das Senden der <name key="Adansonia">Adansonia</name>-Früchte. Solche kommen eben jetz sehr gelegen. Es sind schöne Exemplare. Was kann ich dem jungen Beamten in retour senden?</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bin noch sehr bedrückt mit rückständigen Arbeiten, welche sich während Januar ansammelten. So muss ich mich kurz fassen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Immer Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">24/2/91</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am very grateful to you, dear Mr Tepper, and so also particularly this time to your young son for the consignment of the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Adansonia">Adansonia</name>
               </seg> fruits.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to O. Tepper, 18 February 1890. Tepper had exhibited fruits forwarded by his son from the north-west coast at the meeting of the Royal Society of SA held on 3 February 1891 (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions of the Royal Society of South Australia</seg>, vol. 14, p. 358, 1891; see also <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Express and telegraph</seg> (Adelaide), 4 February 1891, p. 5.</p>
               </note> They come just now at the right time. They are fine specimens. What can I send the young official in return?<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">J. W. O. Tepper was a telegraphist at Roebuck Bay, WA.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am still very burdened with overdue work that accumulated during January. So I must be brief.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Adansonia">Adansonia</name>
            </p>
